channel.title: Looking for another Developer
channel.description:
I currently have a 317 loading 525 data [PI] base online, and I have been the sole coder/developer for a bit, and it is getting stressful and tiring. I am looking for someone to co-develop with me on my 317. Requirements: 1. Must have Decent-Good knowledge of coding 317 2. Must have proof of a previous work/rsps 3. Must have skype 4. Must be willing to help whenever you can 5. Anything else we can discuss over skype.
Check out the server at http://wrathscape.info if you must.. Click play now to get started.
Send me a PM if you are interested and ask for my skype. Thanks in advance!

item.title: Looking for another Developer
item.dc:creator: @Damoiscool Damoiscool
item.description:
@Damoiscool wrote:

Pm’ed you. If you plan on going further with this I think you should re-consider “Kee’s” admin position. Logged in and was given a free purple p hat and d plate (or) and d plate (g). This admin thought he/she was being funny because they didn’t work. So I made up some BS about sending a fake packet to add it to player shops for 1b and the admin started freaking out jailed me, muted me, then ip-banned me while I was posting this. Thought it was pretty funny.
